<span id="freeTextContainer10040629758501138323">To me this is the weakest book in the series. It follows the same formula of the other two, but it just feels worn out. Will just wasn&apos;t too interesting of a character to me. If anything the only part I truly enjoyed was Jane&apos;s cameo. This book is really the only &quot;sequel&quot; in the series, being that Will is a character from the second book. I had hoped we&apos;d see a lot more world building or expansion because of that. But to me it fell short....</span>
