        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3156578312" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18298106635324583041">Delicious. Michael Swanwick is a master wordsmith and story weaver, and wields both to great effect in The Dragons of Babel. A little part of me says &quot;this was a lot of words and plot twists for the payoff&quot; but a much bigger part of me says &quot;hahahaha! totally did not see that coming!&quot; And how often does that happen? So worth it.</span>
  <span id="freeText18298106635324583041" style="display:none">Delicious. Michael Swanwick is a master wordsmith and story weaver, and wields both to great effect in The Dragons of Babel. A little part of me says "this was a lot of words and plot twists for the payoff" but a much bigger part of me says "hahahaha! totally did not see that coming!" And how often does that happen? So worth it.</span>
