  <span id="freeText16170555028046899355" style="display:none">You can tell the author is a great short story teller - sometimes the characters just go off into random stories and it's amazing.<br /><br />Also the worldbuilding is something else. Swanwick does a increadible job of making the world feel real and detailed.</span>
